node.text:
Today we're making Ray-Ban history with @Facebook. ​

Introducing Ray-Ban Stories, our first generation of smart glasses: the new way to capture, share and listen. ​

#RayBanStories​
@Roccobasilico @Zuck

node.text:
Welcome back to the moment. ​

Discover our first generation of smart glasses that keeps you connected. So you can keep your eyes on the world around you. ​

Created in collaboration with @Facebook, #RayBanStories are the new way to capture, share and listen.​
